63
00:05:13,130 --> 00:05:14,500
Let's move him to a bed.

64
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,680
Okay, we're moving you.

65
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,080
Mr. Son Seok Ki.

66
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,120
