67
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,310
Please stay until you're stable.

68
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:33,940
I'll prescribe it right now,
so please be patient.

69
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,950
- Check his vitals.
- Yes, sir.

70
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:41,300
The patient that just arrived...

71
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,860
After she checks his vitals...

72
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:51,300
Please administer
painkiller and antiemetic.

73
00:05:55,730 --> 00:05:57,280
[ 1st round of chemotherapy scheduled ]

74
