Cha Yo Han?

84
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,670
[ Emergency Medical Center ]

85
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,930
How are you feeling?

86
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:12,270
Much better, yes.

87
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:19,750
But earlier...

88
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:20,930
Pardon?

89
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,250
Never mind.

90
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:26,380
If you get these symptoms again,

91
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,840
come to the ER right away.

92
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,840
Okay.

93
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:36,540
Dr. Cha, what are your thoughts
on what a doctor's role is?

94
