Your mom will want
to see you too.

95
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:39,860
Let's go to your mom.

96
00:07:39,860 --> 00:07:43,600
Deciphering what is most
beneficial for a patient...

97
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,670
I think that's a doctor's role.

98
00:07:46,670 --> 00:07:49,630
"The right decisions regarding life?"

99
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,730
Is euthanasia a part of it?

100
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:53,180
Of course, it is.

101
00:07:54,490 --> 00:07:58,240
