aren't always about death.

102
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,180
However...

103
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,520
Mom!

104
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:05,000
What is the most beneficial for
a patient between life and death...

105
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,910
I must give it my all till the end

106
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:09,130
to think over and make
the right decisions.

107
00:08:20,910 --> 00:08:26,140
[ Memento Mori: Latin for an
object symbolizing "death" ]

108
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:43,120
- Yes, Officer.
